//Lung


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 09 of Cardiac MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Lung' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And 'Consolidation' radio button is enabled
And 'Pleural effusion' radio button is enabled
And 'Atelectasis' radio button is enabled
And 'Pulmonary nodule' radio button is enabled
And 'Mass' radio button is enabled
And 'Pneumothorax' radio button is enabled



When I select 'Consolidation' radio button
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Lobar' radio button is enabled
And 'Atypical' radio button is enabled

And 'Atelectasis' radio button is enabled
And 'Dystelectasis' radio button is enabled
And 'Mass' radio button is enabled

When I select all parts on the localizer
Then all parts are selected and turn red

When I select 'Atypical' radio button
Then 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled
And 'Multifocal' radio button is enabled



When I select 'Pleural effusion' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Right' checkbox
Then 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'Distinct' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Left' checkbox
Then 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'Distinct' radio button is enabled



When I select 'Atelectasis' radio button
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Subsegmental' radio button is enabled
And 'Segmental' radio button is enabled
And 'Lobar' radio button is enabled

And 'Triangular' radio button is enabled
And 'String shaped' radio button is enabled
And 'Round' radio button is enabled

And 'Consolidation' radio button is enabled
And 'Mass' radio button is enabled

When I select all parts on the localizer
Then all parts are selected and turn red



When I select 'Pulmonary nodule' radio button
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Maximum diameter axial' input field is enabled
And 'Consolidation' radio button is enabled
And 'Atelectasis' radio button is enabled




When I select 'Mass' radio button
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Maximum diameter axial' input field is enabled
And 'Pleura' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pericardium' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bone' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mediastinum' checkbox is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled



When I select 'Pneumothorax' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Right' checkbox
Then 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'Distinct' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Left' checkbox
Then 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'Distinct' radio button is enabled
